biography: curator of things & connector of people

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I had a great time chatting with Yam & Raph about their project, World of Women, that has taken the NFT world by storm ⚡️

I’ve been supporting it since day 0 and it’s been an amazing journey so far. Prominent names in the NFT space like @garyvee & @loganpaul have also expressed their liking towards WoW 🤩 

In this conversation, we covered :

• how the project came to be 
• yam & raph’a opinion on collecting NFTs
• what it takes to execute a successful marketing strategy 
• general club update + curator’s club experience
• collaborations in the works 
• reaction to prominent folks buying in 
• advice for NFT artists that are just starting out 
• a final note to all holders 

Hope you enjoy this!

If there’s any other projects that you’d like to see me interact with, tag them in comments 💕

Thank you @worldofwomen.nft for your time!
